commits.name: Commit-0
commits.content:
Experience the Freedom to Explore at Chapman University
Ready to unleash your full potential? Fill out the form below to request more information about Chapman University’s bachelor’s degrees.

You know the feeling. That jolt when you’re on to something. When you discover what you’re passionate about. When four hours fly by like four minutes, because you’re doing what you love. The smile spreads across your face and you feel the possibilities unfold.

At Chapman University, that feeling is an entire campus. It’s in everything we do. In everything we’ve been and everything we become. Because at Chapman, our passion is turning yours into a bright future.

Here, we consider ourselves a playground to explore. Join us as we let our hearts lead us to places we never imagined.

Personalized Undergraduate Education
We believe everyone’s education should be different. That’s why we offer small classes (average size: 23 students) and encourage you to study abroad, join research projects, double major and so much more.
Your Home Away From Home
Southern California is one of the most desirable places to live — and we’re in the heart of it all. Find your community on our convenient campus through Chapman’s First Year Experience programs and 190+ student organizations.
Helpful Financial Support
Cost shouldn’t get in the way of following your dreams. This year Chapman invested over $120 million in our students and the average award for Fall 2020 was over $28,000 per student.
Unmatched Research Opportunities
Every new idea started with a simple question: “Why?” At Chapman, embrace your curiosity by participating in undergraduate research that really matters.
Discover a World of Opportunity

Chapman believes it isn't enough to learn about what you love, you need to experience it. We’re here to make something. Do something. Be something. It isn’t about just studying our interests; it’s about uncovering how that passion can be turned into a meaningful profession.

Here, you can join the 50% of students who study abroad. The 50% who engage in life-changing research. The 80% who participate in internships. Through trial, error, testing and practicing, 87% of our students are employed or admitted to graduate school within 6 months of graduation. Because at Chapman, the skills and career services you gain don’t leave you after you graduate. You’re a Panther for life.

We’ve Got the Tools to Thrive

You have the heart, now you just need the skills. Join a university that knows what it takes to make a difference.

  • #4 Best Film School in America, The Wrap
  • #14 Top Private Universities in California, Niche
  • #18 Colleges with the Best Professors in California, Niche
  • #39 Best Undergraduate Teaching in America, U.S. News & World Report
  • #68 Most Innovative Schools in America, U.S. News & World Report
"I see my professors around campus. They not only recognize me, but stop to chat and see how I’m doing. Getting to know faculty helps break down the communication barriers outside and inside the classroom."
- Samir Kamnani, ‘19
Get to Know Chapman University
